\f0\i \'a0of the Spirit of God in your heart;\'a0 all else shall be as the idle wind. \'a0 Reading thus, in absolute dependence, not upon man's wisdom or teaching, but upon the utterances of the blessed Spirit within, you shall infallibly be guided into all Truth.\'a0 Such is the promise of Him who cannot lie. "
\f1\i0\b0 \cb1 \

